Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美奈和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下堂是美术课，快点到教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 额头流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保健室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个粗心的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员的改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么目的潜入美里家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊，原来是SLALLY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫的这么亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真难相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？她现在怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没抓到什么小辫子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我可不象麻幌跟阿优那么容易相信人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要发现什么怪举动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前头，对我来说你还是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候再对我爪牙相向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真难相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时不注意就飞过头到台北去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能吃梅干便当啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样到傍晚就会没力气的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一今天放学后\N跟美里同学展开超级大战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师～老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子又想来我们家打牙祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿石头丢她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的卤萝卜真好吃啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…就爱给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笼包从天而降！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是神明的赏赐不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家的赏赐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，找到了，美奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流河老师…还有史莱修？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…幌！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊—真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼—吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和为什么老是在道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我老是挨骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…不用跟我道歉也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦，怎么了，阿优
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！是软弱无力滚地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒！美奈和，有气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么看…都觉得只是刚好跌到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉啦，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多男孩子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家凑在一起到底要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿优，赶快回攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边线出现空档了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了，阿优！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浜口，你在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在干吗，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式条老师被照明灯压到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没有这么好笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌，你真是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如说是个连普通蜗牛都会当成\N法国蜗牛误食的大笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会搞错那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实那家伙曾经在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了奇怪的蘑菇笑了一整晚差点没挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，不要那么暴力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到…内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和，已经不要紧了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去躺一下休息吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，已经没什么大碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道她是管理者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还收留她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本只会招来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是为了杀你的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客的话从以前就不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:17:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她搞不好有什么目的才来接近你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样也没办法断定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你自己还有疑虑，那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿优他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把那女孩子接到家里来照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌你其实也想要帮助那个女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说麻幌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太白星在这场战争中扮演的是什么角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让地球人跟外星人的战争失控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演着抑制他们的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天让双方互相了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起往同一个未来迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个基础更加坚定的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那意思是中立的角色喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在两方都敌视我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是太可怜了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了不让希望的火苗熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得有人做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理者这组织有多恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌一直都没跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道把管理者的人留在家里会有多么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若对逃离组织的她见死不救的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类非坚持不可的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫370总觉得不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤美奈和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样感觉好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻幌的妹妹会不会过头点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿优…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是太白星的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为疑神疑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了怜悯心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就跟管理员没有两样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道我说这句话实在是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想拜托史莱修跟流河
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们保护阿优吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还欠你人情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会铭记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士之间的约定我一定会遵守的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你选择哪条路\N都会保护你和阿优的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说什么丧气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，史莱修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿优，美奈和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚餐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！是！是！是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不请自来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多吃点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿喜烧～寿喜烧～很好吃喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该放什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，阿优？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点吃就没得吃了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块肉是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜也很好吃，要多吃点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和如果不多吃点肉\N会跟姐姐一样没有胸部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
